You will have to organise your endpoints/resources in separate `&lt;jaxrs:server &gt;` tags with their own settings for attachment size:

```xml
&lt;jaxrs:server id=&quot;services&quot;&gt;
    &lt;jaxrs:properties&gt;
        &lt;entry key=&quot;attachment-max-size&quot; value=&quot;1024&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/jaxrs:properties&gt;
    ....
&lt;/jaxrs:server&gt;


&lt;jaxrs:server id=&quot;largeFileServices&quot;&gt;
    &lt;jaxrs:properties&gt;
        &lt;entry key=&quot;attachment-max-size&quot; value=&quot;1000000&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/jaxrs:properties&gt;
    ....
&lt;/jaxrs:server&gt;
```

